high_descs: Turn left to face counter next to sink.
Pick up knife between pump dispenser and lettuce from counter.
Move down the counter slightly to the left.
Slice apple on the back of the counter.
Turn around to table across room, with microwave on it.
Place knife on table, to the left of the microwave.
Turn around, go to counter with sliced apple on it.
Pick up slice of apple from counter.
Turn around, go to table with microwave and knife on it.
Put apple slice in microwave in front of potato, close door.  Wait three seconds, take apple out of microwave, shut door.
Move slightly to the left.
Put apple on counter left to the blade of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Pick up knife, slice apple, move knife to another table, heat apple slice in microwave and put it on a table.

high_descs: Go to the left of the sink
Pick up the knife from the drying rack
Turn and look at the apple
Cut the apple
Go to the microwave
Put the knife on the plate on the left
Go to the sink
Pick up an apple slice
Go to the microwave
Heat the apple slice
Go slightly to the left
Put the apple down next to the knife
anns.task_desc: Place a heated apple slice and a knife down next to a plate

high_descs: Turn so that you're facing the drying rack to the left of the sink.
Pick up the knife that's on the rack.
Take a tiny step to the left and face the drying rack again.
Use the knife to cut the apple on the drying rack.
Bring the knife with you and turn around, cross the room so that you're facing the black table with the black microwave on it.
Put the knife down on the left side of the table.
Go back over to the drying rack.
Pick up a piece of the sliced apple.
Bring the apple over to the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave and cook it, then pull it back out.
Take a step to the left with the apple.
Put the apple down so that it's to the left of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a piece of apple.
